Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:25.69,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}愛を想う 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:35.11,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}ひとつだけゆずれぬ願い 
